    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to get this absolute beauty into the hands of someone who will love it as much as I have. Honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! Not a single scratch or dent to be found anywhere. It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept, so you\u2019re basically getting a new car for a steal. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
