    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior boasts its original, deep-lustre paint, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely zero imperfections, rock chips, or swirls. Inside, the cabin retains that fresh-from-the-factory scent; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and every tactile surface feels brand new. Mechanically, it is flawless, supported by a comprehensive binder of every service record performed exclusively at certified dealerships. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched alloy wheels, this car is a collector-grade gem that drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
