      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unrivaled pedigree, maintained to an impeccable standard that reflects showroom-grade integrity. This specimen exhibits flawless aesthetic preservation and mechanical excellence, representing the absolute pinnacle of its class. For the discerning enthusiast who demands a curated driving experience, this offering provides a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine automotive asset. Every detail, from the lustrous exterior finish to the untouched interior surfaces, underscores a legacy of meticulous stewardship and uncompromising care.",
